Layout of code

Package  dev  

HeapProfiler.java  	main class runs runs code to create object pools and look at garbage collection
JVMProfiler.java   	main class runs runs code to java.lang.management package to profile the JVM
JvmResearch.java  	main class runs runs the benchmarking code in the dev.benchmarks package
StackProfiler.java 	mani class runs a recursive stack profiling function, will not run on a 64 bit jvm

Package dev.benchmarks

BenchMarkBase.java  super class for benchmarks
ListBenchMark.java and MapBenchMark.java benchmarking code for Java Collections and Maps
MemoryBarrierBenchMark.java, MemoryTest.java, ParallelProcessingBenchMark.java, SynchronizerBenchMark.java
run code to test the Java Memory Model (JMM)

Package dev.dump
Dumper.java  class to perform a thread dump, can be called at any time in the code

package net.rudolfcode.jvm
Example1.java  very simple example to look at memory use of java collections
Example2.java  very simple example to look at memory use of synchronization
Example3.java  example of using java.lang.management package to look at memory use of java collections
Example3A.java example of using java.lang.management package to look at cpu use of java collections


 





